Steelpoort businessman Jeff Mabuza has been identified as the pilot who had tragically died in the light aircraft crash outside Mbombela yesterday afternoon, January 30. Tributes for the well-loved aviator have begun pouring in from friends on Facebook. ALSO READ: Light aircraft crash near old Nelspruit Airfield claims life ALSO READ: Civil Aviation Authority comments on aircraft crash near Mbombela Mabuza is said to have been a passionate pilot with a love of flying, and it was said his death was a huge loss to the aviation world. This is a developing story. Lowvelder will update its readers as soon as more information becomes available.